text: @UPSHelp Two UPS drivers interrupted a client meeting at a professional office space for my company by knocking on a closed conference room door insisting that they needed a signature.  Turns out they were delivering a plant.  It was unprofessional and unacceptable.

@vtsquiggle I apologize for the experience! We can help to address this issue. Please use the link to send us a DM. We'll need your tracking number, delivery address and phone number. ^SK https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
